WEBVTT

00:00:00.386 --> 00:00:07.292
Good morning, family. I have a word for you today. I want you to track back with me.

00:00:07.293 --> 00:00:12.660
A lot of you have been on here for a while, listening to some of the things that I've said.

00:00:12.661 --> 00:00:19.576
Remember the Tasmanian devil coming up out of the pit and the angel unlocking the devil out of that pit?

00:00:19.578 --> 00:00:29.799
It spun up like a Tasmanian devil and had horns on its head. I gave that word—the Lord gave that word to me—about two years ago.

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:40.073
He told me that thing was coming up out of the earth and was being released as a devil of war upon the earth.

00:00:40.074 --> 00:00:59.270
It was spinning and was going to go inside Vladimir Putin. Then I saw a provoking from Poland concerning Ukraine, and that Russia would strike Poland.

00:00:59.271 --> 00:01:22.268
That would be something that we've never seen before. One of the words I'm telling you was to watch for the draft: young men and women both going in a line because of patriotism.

00:01:22.269 --> 00:01:34.437
I'll tell you what I've seen in the spirit. When 9/11 happened, it brought a patriotism upon America.

00:01:34.438 --> 00:02:03.284
The die-hard old country folks, the patriots who love our nation, rose up.

00:02:03.285 --> 00:02:07.520
I have to be very watchful of what I'm saying on this channel now.

00:02:07.521 --> 00:02:30.714
An event is going to happen that is going to cause a great patriotism with certain people, where they will want to go willingly because of what is going to happen.

00:02:30.715 --> 00:02:37.339
We will be hit by another nation; war will happen on American soil.

00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:48.151
I've seen this on the West Coast and in the central part of America.

00:02:48.153 --> 00:03:08.937
I saw ants hidden within cells of people who came across the southern border over the last several years.

00:03:08.938 --> 00:03:27.577
There's more than you realize. When this happens, it's like ants coming out of an anthill.

00:03:27.578 --> 00:03:50.477
They've come for years through the administrations. When this happens, it's going to be another type of 9/11 event.

00:03:50.478 --> 00:04:13.046
Putin went to North Korea, right? It hasn't been done in 25 years. Now he is in Vietnam as I speak.

00:04:13.047 --> 00:04:50.526
I asked the Lord, and He said, 'Brandon, before any major nation declares a major war and retaliates for what that spinning devil did, you have to have allies.'He is bringing forth a coalition of allies to help back him.

00:04:50.527 --> 00:05:05.224
Right now, the BRICS nations are forming a financial coalition so that when the United States tries to put sanctions, he can go around it with Saudi Arabia because they broke the petrodollar deal.

00:05:05.225 --> 00:05:16.905
I told you all it was coming. I saw the Prince MBS put his foot down.

00:05:16.906 --> 00:05:20.453
They were looking for a stronger backbone of leadership in America.

00:05:20.454 --> 00:05:36.227
I saw the Antichrist agenda trying to come on, and they were going to create a new global system with China, Russia, and Saudi Arabia.

00:05:36.228 --> 00:05:54.239
Then I saw it spreading through the OPEC nations—Iran, Iraq, and all the major Middle East—and then it would spread through Africa and South America.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:06:24.360
It kept spreading like the Indiana Jones map. A major war is about to take place.

00:06:24.361 --> 00:06:34.542
It's not just nation fighting against nation; it's going to be like World War II but very nasty.

00:06:34.543 --> 00:06:41.862
This will escalate until the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ and the Rapture of the Church.

00:06:41.863 --> 00:06:45.144
The Lord warned me again last night and said a great humbling will come to the American people, and this will bring a great shaking on America.

00:06:45.145 --> 00:07:24.784
He said the true part of it is the separation of the wheat from the tares.

00:07:24.785 --> 00:07:50.407
There will be a dividing line between those on the Lord's side versus the people who are lukewarm.

00:07:50.408 --> 00:08:40.548
You will see an exposing of corrupt ministers. People in sexual perversion will be exposed and brought to light. There will be a separation of the goats and the sheep.

00:08:40.549 --> 00:08:58.904
The Lord said, 'Never touch this with your mouth.'When they fall and are exposed, do not touch them with your mouth.

00:08:58.905 --> 00:09:23.202
We pray for them, their families, and that God would restore them.

00:09:23.203 --> 00:09:59.238
Woe to those who cause the sheep to stumble. Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first. We're seeing just the beginning.

00:09:59.239 --> 00:10:11.451
You're going to turn on the TV and go, 'Wow,'because of all the compromise and sin in the church.

00:10:11.452 --> 00:10:23.170
God is cleaning some dirty diapers right now. It starts with the head and goes down through the body.

00:10:23.171 --> 00:11:48.123
There is great corruption in homes with sexual perversions. We must pray for a lessening of what's coming.

00:11:48.124 --> 00:11:55.015
The more you intercede as the body of Christ, the more the volume will come down.

00:11:55.016 --> 00:11:59.773
If we do not take our rightful place of authority, we will be held accountable.

00:11:59.774 --> 00:13:00.278
We have to take our place and be in the right place at the right time, preaching and bringing in the harvest.

00:13:00.279 --> 00:13:16.802
I've told you about the 350 million and the plague. I've seen the biological thing that they're making in laboratories.

00:13:16.803 --> 00:14:09.413
I'm a work in progress, but I am determined to eat healthy Whole Foods.

00:14:09.414 --> 00:14:26.292
I told you to watch what would happen with Donald Trump. A year ago, I said he would have trials until late summer 2024.

00:14:26.293 --> 00:15:02.154
It's a distraction, but it actually saves his life because he is in a courthouse instead of out on a stage.

00:15:02.155 --> 00:15:18.387
God has His hand on him. Pray for this nation, the peace of Jerusalem, and guidance over our land.

00:15:18.388 --> 00:16:35.042
The remnant will rise up and be the salt. We are not people of fear. Birthing pains are taking place all around us.

00:16:35.043 --> 00:16:50.964
The Lord told me that the water is about to get turned off, and you're going to have to start praying over the jet streams and the low-pressure systems.

00:16:50.965 --> 00:17:15.817
Call them forth. There is great weather manipulation going on right now through scientific things.

00:17:15.818 --> 00:18:26.005
It's real. We have authority over the weather and should use it every day. I intercede for the weather all the time.

00:18:26.006 --> 00:18:32.011
Pray for peace, that there won't be terrorist activities, and that every evil plot will be brought to light.

00:18:32.012 --> 00:19:15.036
I pray that my family is always in the right place at the right time and that no calamity comes nigh them.

00:19:15.037 --> 00:19:32.510
I saw the West Coast being struck with war. I saw a surprise attack on Hawaii, similar to Pearl Harbor.

00:19:32.511 --> 00:19:52.538
It was bad, with people running and jets attacking the military bases.

00:19:52.539 --> 00:29:28.518
Let's pray for America. Mercy, Father. Mercy over America. The eyes of our understanding will be enlightened.

00:29:28.519 --> 00:29:35.838
The eyes of the Lord run to and fro looking for a heart that is perfect towards Him.

00:29:35.839 --> 00:29:50.333
We stand on Your word. You will supply all our needs according to Your riches and glory.

00:29:50.334 --> 00:30:16.735
We call forth financial breakthrough and speak blessing and increase. We take authority over poverty and lack.

00:30:16.736 --> 00:30:31.382
We thank You, Lord, that You have the cattle on a thousand hills to always take care of us.

00:30:31.383 --> 00:30:45.308
We call forth financial freedom and overflow, exceedingly abundantly above all that they dare ask or think.

00:30:45.309 --> 00:31:26.744
We call for healing and wholeness. We command people to be free from addictions, drugs, alcohol, and perversion.

00:31:26.745 --> 00:31:28.719
We break the spirit of rebellion in children and grandchildren.

00:31:28.720 --> 00:33:41.522
We call for fresh fire on our homes and marriages. No more torment in sleep.

00:33:41.523 --> 00:38:08.464
Denominational barriers are coming down. I sense there's so much He wants to give.

00:38:08.465 --> 00:38:49.039
There are many spiritual rooms and doors. By the words of a minister, those doors will open.

00:38:49.040 --> 00:40:42.790
Father, we open the doors by faith. Create in us a clean heart, oh God.

00:40:42.791 --> 00:41:16.109
We want to be at the spout where the glory comes out. Come up higher in your prayer life.

00:41:16.110 --> 00:42:35.813
Let the Holy Spirit flow like a mighty river out of our bellies.

00:42:35.814 --> 00:43:08.895
Arise and shine, for the light has come. The joy of the Lord is our strength.

00:43:08.896 --> 00:46:33.070
We bind depression, anxiety, fear, and worry. We call for a harvest of souls like this world has never seen.

00:46:33.071 --> 00:47:17.563
We call forth our unsaved loved ones to be born again. There is a tsunami-sized wave of the outpouring coming.

00:47:17.564 --> 00:48:12.617
I've seen it. Our prayers are drawing the wave in. We will see an October outpouring that will hit with such ferocity.

00:48:12.618 --> 00:48:35.067
The church is taking on the model of Heaven on Earth. There is a wave of glory.

00:48:35.068 --> 00:49:26.822
We call forth a shaking of your people; we call forth awakening.

00:49:26.823 --> 00:49:55.962
Wake up, it's time! Jesus is coming. We thank You for the fresh manifestations of the glory.

00:49:55.963 --> 00:51:48.432
It's going to hit the street corners and the White House. We are going to overflow.

00:51:48.433 --> 00:52:00.746
Jesus is faithful. Put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:52:00.747 --> 00:52:14.960
Jesus loves you. Have a wonderful day. God bless you. Bye-bye.

